                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You bring up a good question Aithur.  People using roleplaying as an excuse for poor behavior.  I personally think all the RP crap should be tossed out the window in most PvP situations.  It's not orc vs human, it's human vs human.  As in it's another human being behind the controls of your enemy.  Sure you want them dead, but do you want to kill them in a way that "ruins" the fun for your fellow human.
<br />

<br />
I guess it amounts to PvP at the expense of others?  Or, PvP fun for all.
<br />

<br />
On a side note I ran into a 33 dwarf hunter in Hillsbrad last night and at 28 I killed him twice.  Dumbass tried to corpse camp me.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />WoW > EQ
<br />
WoW > EQ2
<br />
Blizzard > SOE
