                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">well.. I play WoW for its storyline as much as anything else.. I like good lore.
<br />

<br />
if I just wanted to kill human vs human.. I would go play a FPS.
<br />

<br />
im not their to 'ruin' anything for anyone.. im there to add an extra challenge to the game.
<br />

<br />
I had a good duel with a little gnome mage the other day.. I bowed to his dead body after he died... and undead can still have honor.
<br />

<br />
most people jump on people and try to be snide.. I find that extremely distasteful on both sides.. what they point of being arrogant about killing someone.. especially when a bunch of other people just helped you do it .. and most likely the same thing is gonna happen to you very soon? haha.
<br />

<br />
I have no tolerance for ignorant or rude people.. whatever they are playing/doing. 
<br />

<br />
pvp is not griefing to me.  griefing is ripping out everything the game is and purely being there to hinder someone from playing the game in any way intended.  if someone is there simply to pay a monthly fee just to aggravate other people.. then they should probably go back to bnet :/</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=849817" target="_blank" class="postlink">Aithur the Enchanter (69)</a> [<span style="color: blue">Retired</span>]
