                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I think this depends a lot on what server you are on.  If you are on a PvP server, then I think you can 'get away with' a lot more than if you are on a PvE server in large part because of the rules, but also because no one playing on a PvP server is doing so thinking that they are totally safe from the opposing faction.  Folks who trick people into getting PvP flagged for the purposes of ganging up on them or corpse camping them have crossed a much clearer line in terms of bad PvP ettiquette.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?37749" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.blaynesucks.com/images/Bellanfear.gif" border="0" /></a>
